The '''1997 Nebraska Cornhuskers football team''' represented the [[University of NebraskaâLincoln]] in the [[1997 NCAA Division I-A football season]]. The team was coached by [[Tom Osborne]] and played their home games in [[Memorial Stadium, Lincoln|Memorial Stadium]] in [[Lincoln, Nebraska]].

